OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, fine
OL,6,Fevening, though remaining windy. A
OL,7,Fclear night will follow, and becoming
OL,8,Fchilly in any well sheltered inland
OL,9,Fspots. Winds abating a little, though
OL,10,Fa fresh breeze persisting.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FFine, dry and sunny, though
OL,13,Frather windy once again, with the
OL,14,Fstrongest winds around coasts and
OL,15,Facross hills. Warm, perhaps locally
OL,16,Fvery warm, inland but cooler along the
OL,17,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
